Value PSU (\S+\s+\d+)
Value Model (\S+)
Value Serial (\S+)
Value Voltage (\S+)
Value Current (\S+)
Value Power (\S+)
Value Status (NOT PRESENT|PRESENT|OK|NOT OK)
Value LED (\S+)


Start 
  ^${PSU}\s+${Model}\s+${Serial}\s+${Voltage}\s+${Current}\s+${Power}\s+${Status}\s+${LED} -> Record
  ^Error.* -> Error "Error: fail to get psu status from state DB" -> Record
